<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/23 Very high’ odds of war with China / Should we get married? (host:Larry)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=711&amp;p=739#p739"><![CDATA[
3/23 Very high’ odds of war with China / Should we get married? (host:Larry)<br /><br />We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br /><br />Meeting time agenda:7:00-9:00 PM<br />7:00-7:30 Chatting time with your favorite drink, and introduction of the meeting by the host<br />7:30-8:00 discussion of the first topic<br />8:00-8:05 Take a group photo<br />8:05-8:30 discussion of the second topic<br />8:30-9:00 table topic session (Whenever a question asked, the speaker is given 2 minutes for the impromptu presentation. Each table can use a cell phone as the timer.)<br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 1</span><br />Very high’ odds of war with China, US Republican warns<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2023/1/29/odds-of-military-conflict-with-china-very-high-says-us-official">https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2023/1/2 ... s-official</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.The U. S. predicts that the China will attack Taiwan in 2025. If it’s true, how will you respond? Are you willing to fight for Taiwan if necessary? why and why not?<br />2.Is this war really inevitable? If it happened, can you imagine what the result would be in Taiwan?<br />3.If you were the leader of Taiwan, how would you deal with the current problems?     <br />4.From a historical perspective, do you see the US as a peacekeeper or warmaker, why?<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 2</span><br />Should we get married?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.relate.org.uk/get-help/should-we-get-married">https://www.relate.org.uk/get-help/shou ... et-married</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Question<br />1.What does marriage mean to you? If you are looking for a marriage partner, what are your requirements?<br />2.Do you know why is falling in love easy and getting along hard?<br />3.What do you think are the pros and cons of being married or not?<br />4.Do you think it’s a good idea to have a trial marriage before getting married, and why?  <br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Fri Mar 17, 2023 9:36 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
